snippet.title: Hanna in a Choppa 3 - Trailer
snippet.description:
Take flight in the latest instalment of the hugely popular Hanna in a Choppa series of games. This time, in VR on the Rift and Quest, rather than crappy old Flash. Guide Hanna through 10 bonkers levels each with hidden secrets and achievements.

Get it on App Lab:
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3599849596718662

Join the Discord:
https://discord.gg/cVw7frwNSk
